## Intent

This repository is an infrastructure-heavy reference scaffold for a Symfony/PHP service. The generated output mirrors the bundled reference ZIP and is useful as a baseline for Docker, GitHub Actions, quality tooling, and security controls.

## Important Constraints

- The actual application source is expected under `project/`.
{% if use_docker %}
- `docker-compose.yml` mounts `./project` into the PHP-FPM and nginx containers.
{% endif %}
{% if use_ci %}
- Several deploy jobs reference external reusable workflows from `publicplan-internal/.github`; treat those as organization-specific integration points.
- Local GitHub Actions are referenced via `./.github/actions/...` and each job checks out the repository before using them.
{% endif %}

## Key Areas

{% if use_ci %}
- `.github/actions/`: local composite actions for scanning, build, tagging, and running make targets
- `.github/workflows/pipeline.yml`: CI/CD orchestration for scans, image builds, tests, signing, and deploy hooks
